1
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,680
You saw it just now.

2
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:54,650
What if he has lingering side effects?

3
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,640
What if he becomes disabled?

4
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,600
Who exactly harmed whom?

5
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,480
Tell me.

6
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:07,760
Go tell Gu Xinrui,

7
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,720
I don't accept her apology,

8
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,810
and money is completely unnecessary.

9
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,680
Let her be educated by the law,

10
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,520
and properly turn over a new leaf.

11
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,180
Otherwise, a bigger disaster

12
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:23,440
will make her regret it for life.

13
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:29,760
I understand.

14
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:32,600
I'm sorry.

15
00:02:35,200 --> 00:02:36,800
I shouldn't have come today.

16
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,079
I'm sorry.

17
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,920
The doctor said you need more rest,

18
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:59,200
so you can get better.

19
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:01,600
Grandma has been discharged and gone home.

20
00:03:01,600 --> 00:03:02,360
Don't worry.

21
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,320
She doesn't know we're injured.

22
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,880
We only told her

23
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:09,100
that you accompanied me to Shanghai for a competition.

24
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,920
I'm going to school today.

25
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,960
I'll tutor you when I get back.

26
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,060
Gong Yu, do you want to join us?

27
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,320
Just tutor him.

28
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,880
I recover slowly if I listen to classes.

29
00:03:22,040 --> 00:03:23,920
Then you must listen to the doctor carefully

30
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:24,960
and take your medicine.

31
00:03:24,960 --> 00:03:25,690
Don't worry.

32
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,680
I will help you take good care of him.

33
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,760
With you taking care of him,

34
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,020
I'm even more worried.

35
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,660
Fine. I can't be bothered anyway.

36
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:34,700
Are you going to school alone?

37
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:36,240
That won't do.

38
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,520
Let me go with you.

39
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,000
Nonsense.

40
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,920
Just take good care of yourself.

41
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,280
Mr. Mu will drive me.

42
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,320
Don't worry.

43
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,640
I'm leaving.

44
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:55,140
Blockhead.

45
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,360
With you around,

46
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:01,000
I have never been afraid.

47
00:04:10,760 --> 00:04:11,690
With you around,

48
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,440
I have never been afraid.

49
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:34,360
Yuanbao, ever since your accident,

50
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,520
Meng Jingu applied to Mr. Tian

51
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:39,420
and took over Qingyun's previous position.

52
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:41,200
I think

53
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:43,640
he just doesn't know how to make it up to you,

54
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:45,360
let alone how to face you.

55
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,140
I've never seen him like this.

56
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,800
He's always avoiding us now.

57
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:51,240
He's not even participating in the basketball game.

58
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,800
He and Mutou both quit.

59
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:56,100
So who's going to play in the game now?

60
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,040
It's all my fault.

61
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,880
Don't think like that, Yuanbao.

62
00:05:01,880 --> 00:05:03,640
You and Mu Qingyun are both victims.

63
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,160
Yeah.

64
00:05:04,280 --> 00:05:06,160
But Qingyun is really amazing.

65
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,640
He truly deserves to be the top guy in Zhicheng.

66
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:10,170
Going in single-handedly.

67
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:11,560
So loyal.

68
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,520
Of course.

69
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:15,160
I read Qingyun's fortune a long time ago.

70
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,720
You know what?

71
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,880
His face shows

72
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,850
that he's affectionate and loyal.

73
00:05:18,960 --> 00:05:19,960
More importantly,

74
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:22,160
he will definitely achieve fame and wealth

75
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,360
and enjoy great fortune in the future.

76
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:25,640
Master, read my fortune too.

77
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:28,080
Do I have the face to achieve fame and wealth

78
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,840
and enjoy great fortune in the future?

79
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,440
You?

80
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:35,180
You'll be a nouveau riche at best.

81
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:38,840
Recently, a bullying incident

82
00:05:38,840 --> 00:05:40,800
in a middle school in our city

83
00:05:40,880 --> 00:05:43,320
has aroused widespread public discussion.

84
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,850
Many viewers and netizens,

85
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:47,400
apart from caring about the incident itself,

86
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:49,120
are more concerned about whether the offending students

87
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,800
should bear corresponding legal responsibilities.

88
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,320
Today,

89
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:54,040
our station has invited a professional lawyer

90
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,640
to analyze

91
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,450
middle school bullying for us.

92
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:00,680
Now let's connect with Lawyer Guo.

93
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:02,800
Hello, Lawyer Guo.

94
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:05,000
It seems Gu Xinrui

95
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,740
really caused a huge disaster this time.

96
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:08,600
Yuanbao,

97
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,400
how will you choose to handle it?

98
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:19,920
Yuanbao,

99
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,480
after school,

100
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:23,280
are you going to see Qingyun?

101
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,000
I'm going to tutor him.

102
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:31,000
Can I go with you?

103
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,460
You want to see Gong Yu, right?

104
00:06:37,200 --> 00:06:38,040
No.

105
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,480
How could I?

106
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:41,400
Can I?

107
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:44,640
Fine, you can come with me.

108
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,080
Okay.

109
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:02,520
What's wrong?

110
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,760
Nothing.

111
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,520
Gong Yu.

112
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,080
Nothing.

113
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,930
I need to go to the bathroom.

114
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,740
Why are you asking me for help?

115
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:19,970
Who else would I ask?

116
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,920
Ask the nurse.

117
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,600
The nurse is a girl.

118
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,160
How could she help me take off my pants?

119
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:25,400
Your Yuanbao said

120
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,360
I shouldn't take care of you,

121
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,120
and to let her help you when she gets here.

122
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,640
Yuanbao is also a girl.

123
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:31,330
What about your dad?

124
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:33,460
My dad went to pick her up from school.

125
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,060
What does it have to do with me?

126
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,080
I'm begging you.

127
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,400
Help me.

128
00:07:56,920 --> 00:08:00,320
Hurry up, bro.

129
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:18,680
Ruirui and I just went to buy you some food.

130
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:21,520
Thanks.

131
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:24,780
You guys talk. I'll go get some fresh air.

132
00:08:26,400 --> 00:08:27,680
If you need to pee again,

133
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,740
call me to help you.

134
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,440
You can help with that?

135
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:42,039
His arm is in a cast.

136
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,039
It's hard for him to use the bathroom.

137
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:46,000
You... You helped him?

138
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,680
Who else? Will you?

139
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:50,360
No, no, no. You do it.

140
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:55,130
Stop imagining things.

141
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,720
No, no, no. I'm not.

142
00:08:59,520 --> 00:09:00,920
Do you want me to push you?

143
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,160
No, thanks.

144
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:19,880
Yuanbao.

145
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,320
I know this incident

146
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:26,200
has brought great physical and psychological trauma

147
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,900
to both you and Mu Qingyun.

148
00:09:29,040 --> 00:09:30,280
As your teacher,

149
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,690
I failed to protect you.

150
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,040
I'm sorry.

151
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,720
Similarly,

152
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,800
as Gu Xinrui's teacher,

153
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,720
I failed to educate her well.

154
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,640
I also feel very ashamed.

155
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:44,440
Mr. Tian, how can you be blamed for this?

156
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:48,960
Instead, I often cause trouble

157
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,560
and make you worry.

158
00:09:50,800 --> 00:09:52,130
Regarding this matter,

159
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:54,290
I won't give you any advice.

160
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,760
Whether you choose to settle or not

161
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,780
is entirely up to you and your family.

162
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:06,240
But that day,

163
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,000
I received this.

164
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:11,050
I wasn't supposed to show it to you now.

165
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,560
But after seeing it,

166
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:14,730
I took the liberty to decide

167
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:17,240
that it's better to let you know in advance.

168
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:41,000
Hello. I'd like to ask,

169
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,000
are these lucky stars

170
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,200
for making wishes?

171
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:45,000
Yes, they are new arrivals.

172
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:46,120
We have luminous ones

173
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,120
and regular ones.

174
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:48,960
There are many patterns to choose from,

175
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:51,240
like zodiac signs, horoscopes,

176
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,480
blood types, anime...

177
00:10:52,480 --> 00:10:53,400
We have all kinds.

178
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:54,320
Which one do you want?

179
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:55,780
I can open it for you to see.

180
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:58,730
How many do I need to fold to make a wish?

181
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:00,440
Different amounts have different meanings.

182
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:02,300
It's explained in detail inside.

183
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,620
Look at this question.

184
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:09,080
It has options A and B.

185
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:12,440
Then it's making a sentence with 'because',

186
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:13,800
so...

187
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:21,680
Are you tired?

188
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:24,640
Let's call it a day.

189
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,280
Not tired.

190
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:31,960
Usually when you hear about tutoring,

191
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,760
doesn't it give you a headache?

192
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:34,800
Why are you so well-behaved today?

193
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:35,530
No headache?

194
00:11:37,160 --> 00:11:38,290
No, it doesn't hurt.

195
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:39,840
Because you explained it well,

196
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,570
so I was completely engrossed.

197
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,320
Really?

198
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:44,040
Then tell me,

199
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,240
where was I?

200
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:49,780
This question.

201
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,600
I talked about this question ages ago.

202
00:11:52,920 --> 00:11:54,480
You weren't engrossed.

203
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:56,320
I think you were zoning out.

204
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,680
By the way, Mutou,

205
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:06,160
do you think going to juvie

206
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,240
is a terrifying thing?

207
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,490
Why ask this all of a sudden?

208
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:13,440
Nothing, just asking.

209
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:18,360
Were Gu Xinrui and Brother Shui sentenced?

210
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:21,120
Not yet. Not that fast.

211
00:12:22,680 --> 00:12:24,360
But...

212
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,800
Here is the current situation.

213
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:20,440
Xinrui only instigated them to intimidate Xiong Yuanbao,

214
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,120
and did not ask them to hit anyone.

215
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:24,440
Otherwise, the consequences would be very serious.

216
00:13:24,440 --> 00:13:26,360
Although she can be released on bail for now,

217
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,720
we still need to

218
00:13:27,800 --> 00:13:29,840
negotiate with the victim's family later

219
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:32,120
so that we might reduce the penalty.

220
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:34,000
All right. I understand.

221
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,000
Thank you for your hard work.

222
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:37,000
Okay, Mr. Gu. I'll take my leave now.

223
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,660
Do you know how much effort

224
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:44,960
I put into this for you?

225
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:47,520
I have done my utmost for you.

226
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:48,960
Mom, I...

227
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,640
I really know I was wrong.

228
00:13:51,480 --> 00:13:52,610
You are grown up now.

229
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,240
You need to take responsibility for your actions.

230
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,080
Tomorrow I will send someone

231
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:58,720
to take you back to school to go through the withdrawal procedures.

232
00:13:58,720 --> 00:14:00,200
After this matter is resolved,

233
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,240
you will go back to the UK.

234
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,720
I don't want to see you ever again.

235
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:03,280
Mom,

236
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:04,600
what did you say?

237
00:14:05,520 --> 00:14:06,760
Mom, I was wrong.

238
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,420
Please don't send me away.

239
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,560
I won't dare do it again.

240
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:10,680
I promise to be good.

241
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:11,800
I swear, okay?

242
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,400
I'm getting married next month.

243
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:21,500
I gave you such a superior material life,

244
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:23,700
but failed to enrich your spirit.

245
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,080
Look at what you've done.

246
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,890
You really embarrassed me.

247
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:29,960
How could I...

248
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:31,120
How could I have

249
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,320
such a disappointing daughter like you?

250
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,040
Forget it.

251
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:36,440
You'll be eighteen soon.

252
00:14:36,880 --> 00:14:40,480
You'll have to take responsibility for your own life from now on.

253
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:41,960
This kind of mess,

254
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,320
I will only

255
00:14:44,040 --> 00:14:45,760
clean up for you this one time in my life.

256
00:14:45,760 --> 00:14:47,420
If you cause any more trouble,

257
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:49,000
I won't care anymore.

258
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,040
You take her home first.

259
00:14:51,040 --> 00:14:52,300
I have something to do.

260
00:14:52,920 --> 00:14:54,080
Watch yourself.

261
00:15:03,280 --> 00:15:04,080
Auntie.

262
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,400
Yuanbao.

263
00:15:11,920 --> 00:15:14,120
Can we talk?

264
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:29,080
Child.

265
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,620
I really need to apologize to you.

266
00:15:32,120 --> 00:15:33,650
I know words aren't enough.

267
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:39,090
How are you recovering?

268
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:41,040
Is Mu Qingyun doing okay?

269
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,360
I'm much better.

270
00:15:42,920 --> 00:15:44,200
But Mu Qingyun

271
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:46,800
still needs to be observed in the hospital.

272
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:49,010
I'm really sorry to both of you.

273
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:51,360
I failed to raise my son well.

274
00:15:52,120 --> 00:15:53,480
Making you endure all this

275
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,680
at such a young age.

276
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:56,640
Auntie.

277
00:15:57,480 --> 00:15:58,800
I came to find you today

278
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:02,120
because I actually have something to tell you.

279
00:16:02,120 --> 00:16:02,960
Go ahead.

280
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:16,400
Yuanbao, Mu Qingjun.

281
00:16:17,840 --> 00:16:19,040
This is what Gu Xinrui

282
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:21,280
asked the police to hand over to me.

283
00:16:21,280 --> 00:16:24,280
She wanted me to wait until she finished her punishment

284
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:25,240
and left the city

285
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,650
before giving it to you.

286
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:28,120
But as a teacher,

